<code><a href="{@docRoot}guide/topics/manifest/provider-element.html#gprmns">grantUriPermissions</a></code>
attribute of the 
<code><a href="{@docRoot}guide/topics/manifest/provider-element.html">&lt;provider&gt;</a></code> 
element</dd>


</dl>
